General Assembly Senate Joint
Resolution No. 4
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1217
Referred to Committee on EXECUTIVE AND LEGISLATIVE
NOMINATIONS
Introduced by:
SEN. DUFF, 25th Dist.
REP. CONCEPCION, 4th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF HARRY RILLING
OF NORWALK TO BE A MEMBER OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS
OF THE CONNECTICUT PORT AUTHORITY.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by Bob Duff, the majority leader of the Senate,
2 of Harry Rilling of Norwalk to be a member of the Board of Directors of
3 the Connecticut Port Authority, for a term ending June 30, 2029, is
4 hereby approved and confirmed.
